      "content"	 : "I thought I‚Äôd post a short update about why I haven‚Äôt been blogging as much.These past two months have been a whirlwind for me. I am looking for jobs and I have gotten some interest. I can‚Äôt say too much right now, but things are looking up.The tweets that started it:https://twitter.com/TiffanyW_412/status/922997615230357505It was during a #DevDiscuss Twitter chat. Initially, Pablo Rivera tweeted to Stephanie Hurlburt about getting me a job. She tweeted back to tweet to her my portfolio, resume, etc and that I am looking for work. She would then retweet it to her large following of potential employers and companies.I did:https://twitter.com/TiffanyW_412/status/923000005035724800And awesome‚Ä¶things‚Ä¶started‚Ä¶happening.I thought I‚Äôd post a short update about why I haven‚Äôt been blogging as much.These past two months have been a whirlwind for me. I am looking for jobs and I have gotten some interest. I can‚Äôt say too much right now, but things are looking up.The tweets that started it:https://twitter.com/TiffanyW_412/status/922997615230357505It was during a #DevDiscuss Twitter chat. Initially, Pablo Rivera tweeted to Stephanie Hurlburt about getting me a job. She tweeted back to tweet to her my portfolio, resume, etc and that I am looking for work. She would then retweet it to her large following of potential employers and companies.I did:https://twitter.com/TiffanyW_412/status/923000005035724800And awesome‚Ä¶things‚Ä¶started‚Ä¶happening.That‚Äôs all I can really say but I have honestly just been trying to process what is happening and how, when it comes together and tries, the tech community is the best there is‚Ä¶",
