    "working-chrome-devtools": {
      "title": "Working With Chrome DevTools",
      "content"	 : "After working with web dev technologies for the past two years, I am finally beginning to understand the virtues of developer tools, specifically Chrome DevTools 1.Intimidated by the ‚ÄòToolsFor a while now I had been intimidated by all the tabs and functions of the Chrome DevTools 2. But as I became a better developer 3 I began to use DevTools to debug my apps. The more I worked with them, the more fearless I became.Some Interesting, Basic Things You Can Do with the ‚ÄòToolsPlaying with the HTMLThe nice thing about DevTools is that whatever you play with inside of them, it really doesn‚Äôt affect the site you‚Äôre playing with.Here I can add a class on an element 4 and hit return. It adds the class.https://i.imgur.com/DZMZiDR.gifvChanging StylesHere you can just play around with the styles on the site. Here, I change the color of the text on Packt Pub to a color called Disco.[embed]https://i.imgur.com/5MJDBLd.gifv[/embed]¬†Maybe Some More DevTools Content?I think I will make a series out of this. What do you think?After working with web dev technologies for the past two years, I am finally beginning to understand the virtues of developer tools, specifically Chrome DevTools 1.Intimidated by the ‚ÄòToolsFor a while now I had been intimidated by all the tabs and functions of the Chrome DevTools 2. But as I became a better developer 3 I began to use DevTools to debug my apps. The more I worked with them, the more fearless I became.Some Interesting, Basic Things You Can Do with the ‚ÄòToolsPlaying with the HTMLThe nice thing about DevTools is that whatever you play with inside of them, it really doesn‚Äôt affect the site you‚Äôre playing with.Here I can add a class on an element 4 and hit return. It adds the class.https://i.imgur.com/DZMZiDR.gifvChanging StylesHere you can just play around with the styles on the site. Here, I change the color of the text on Packt Pub to a color called Disco.[embed]https://i.imgur.com/5MJDBLd.gifv[/embed]¬†Maybe Some More DevTools Content?I think I will make a series out of this. What do you think?            I can definitely argue they are the best around. Safari, on the Mac is probably the worst, but then, Apple has no incentive to give web developers tools because it won‚Äôt help their bottom line, i.e. App Store.¬†&amp;#8617;¬†&amp;#8617;2              Hackers hack: I spent my late teens and early twenties just playing around with Windows, not being scared of breaking things. Not sure why I didn‚Äôt just play around with the tools.¬†&amp;#8617;¬†&amp;#8617;2              And watched countless tutorials‚Ä¶¬†&amp;#8617;¬†&amp;#8617;2              It‚Äôs really a ridiculous class: page-id? I was stumped while making the gif. Ha.¬†&amp;#8617;¬†&amp;#8617;2      ",
      "url": " /working-chrome-devtools",
      "tags": "Developer Tools, developers, web development"
    }
