. Will be doing that from now on.This is Hard‚Ä¶The price of success is hard work, dedication to the job at hand, and the determination that whether we win or lose, we have applied the best of ourselves to the task at hand. ‚Äì Vince Lomabardi‚Ä¶As it should be. Programming isn‚Äôt easy. I‚Äôve hit a bump, a snag, the honeymoon not as great as before but I still love it. I love it when my code just works. I may have had to iterate a million times and I may have introduced 10 more bugs than I had before in the source code but it is so worth it to see the end result.Here is a gist of one of my solutions. You‚Äôre free to refactor.¬†https://gist.github.com/twhite96/d093f42db2954b8a84a7#file-bonfire_longest_word-js¬†¬†¬†¬†",
